{"tid":1213014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家唔好氣餒，呢個係我哋一整代人嘅長期抗爭","createTime":"2019-06-13T00:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T01:04:33.000Z","uid":158504,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8c52f0daa7751cf2e902bb89ed4145e9a01de6","tid":1213014,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:03:22.000Z","msg":"見到好多人經過呢禮拜<br />\n開始氣餒<br />\n質疑自己 質疑個運動值唔值得<br />\n絕對係值得<br />\n一定要堅持住信念 哪怕好多挫折<br />\n面對獨裁打壓 抗爭會係持久 痛苦<br />\n台灣 韓國 好多抗爭20 30 40年先見到曙光<br />\n如果連自己都放棄自己 就以後冇人救到你<br />\n望望中國<br />\n成班後生行屍走肉吃喝玩樂<br />\n連出街叫一聲反對嘅膽都冇<br />\n我絕對唔甘心變到佢地咁垃圾<br />\n<br />\n上一代 好好彩有英國人為佢地擋風擋雨 冇政治抗爭嘅洗禮<br />\n我地身處呢個時代 就注定條路難行<br />\n上一代香港人缺席嘅政治課 由我哋呢代補上<br />\n希望大家記住呢幾日種感覺 不忘初心 唔好放棄"},{"pid":"9871f649750fd7fb45cee2e0c75f2ae4a5ef0ef0","tid":1213014,"uid":259736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6527cd699520fe9ea0d460fb5bc8a129f280cd4","tid":1213014,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:28:11.000Z","msg":"香港人善忘，但呢段日子一定一定會記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">立會前，搵返自己嘅初心：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">【致瞓唔着嘅巴絲：當你迷茫絕望之時】我地到底係為咩而捨命抗爭？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"90311b44df0017bdfc75967530ec1df13e70f262","tid":1213014,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T00:43:06.000Z","msg":"失敗之後我日日係地鐵閘口範圍飲汽水 然後仆低"},{"pid":"47a871916a30efac79549614a2d0a758fcf051ec","tid":1213014,"uid":60764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":